  "notes": "First flight date is the H3-22 configuration's maiden flight, the family's first. Flight totals are split across H3-22/24/30 configurations in Launch Library, so no aggregate is recorded. Weekly maintenance 2026-07-13: LL2 rate-limited this run (429 on first call, stopped per budget rule). last_flight_date corrected from 2025-12-22 to 2026-06-12 (JAXA flight No.6, the boosterless H3-30S debut) using JAXA's own first-party press release, already the source for the matching events-list entry; the field had gone stale relative to the events already on file. flights_total (8) and flights_successful (6), sourced from Wikipedia as_of 2026-07-05 (after the June flight), already appear to include it per the SpaceNews item in items.json (id 2026-06-12-jaxa-h3-30s-first-flight, which counts the June 12 flight as H3's eighth overall); left unchanged, not independently re-verified this run. next_flight_date (2026-08-06, LL as_of 2026-07-05) not re-checked (LL unreachable); left as-is.",
